majorIds.Sun Eater: +Sun Eater: Failing to backstab an enemy from behind blinds them for 2s and slows them by 20% for 5s.

add.lore: The sun fears its wings, and so shall your enemies.

majorIds.Self-sufficient: +Self-sufficient: Powder Specials can no longer be charged manually, but accumulate 7% charge every second.

add.lore: This pendant is not much more than a battery on a string, but a curious combination of Avos and electromagic seem to have left it with the ability to charge power from its surroundings on its own.

after.lore: Unspeakable things live within the shadows; waiting so patiently to take others into their ranks. Facsimiles of their existence, painted in inscrutable darkness. Nobody will see. Nobody will know. Nobody will remember.
